data.description: Great tri-level w 2.5 car attached garage in Gracefield Subd. This immaculate home feats 3 bedrooms, 2 baths & large family room with wood burning fireplace. Bright living room w beautiful carbonized strand bamboo hardwood floors that stretch through main level. Custom cabinetry & Corinne countertops embellish kitchen. Dining room overlooks fenced in backyard with heated inground swimming pool, storage shed & concrete patio. Other upgrades include roof, siding, sliding glass door, windows, gutters and landscaping. This is a must-see property.
